caption:
NEWS! 🚨🇮🇳 Single-seater star @jehand98 joins Mahindra Racing!

The 24-year-old Indian racer joins the team as Reserve Driver, also working on the development of the car as we enter the #Gen3 era ⚡️

Find out more via link in bio 🔗

Aaahhhh, this one hurts😖 But still a P2 finish🏆... I had an awesome start to get into the lead and then just managed the race from there until the safety cars… The car was great all race but a small lock up on the restart cost us the win today. Onto tomorrow 👊🏽

📸 @jamesgasperotti 

#RedBull #RedBullJuniorTeam #Prema #PAP #Winway #F2 #BellRacingHQ #AzerbaijanGP

What a couple of days it’s been!… An unreal experience driving a Formula 1 car for the first time around Silverstone 🤩👌🏽 A big thank you again to everyone that made this happen, I had lots of fun and learned so much in just two days ✅

📸 photos by @nickdunganphoto 

#Formula1 #F1 #F1Testing #Silverstone #McLaren

Yesss!! P1 🏆 Got the lead at the start and then it was just about managing the tyres and the pace… looking to repeat the same tomorrow ✅ Hearing the national anthem on the top step of the Monza podium feels really special 😀 … Big thanks to @carlinracing for the mega car 💪🏽

📸 James Gasperotti 

#redbull #redbulljuniorteam #carlin #pap #winway #f2 #ItalianGP

P1!!😀✅...Feels really good to end the season on a high..A big thank you to team💪🏼 and everyone who’s supported me throughout the season ...See you next year😉 #redbulljuniorteam #carlin #f2 #pap #winway

Yesss, P1!🏆… A big thanks to the boys and girls @prema_team - the car was rapid and the pit-stop amazing ✅ 

Feels good to go into the break with a double podium under my belt!💪🏽

📸 @jamesgasperotti 

#RedBull #RedBullJuniorTeam #Prema #PAP #Winway #F2 #BellRacingHQ #ItalianGP

Super excited and grateful for the opportunity to have my first experience in a Formula 1 car testing with McLaren this week!😀
A big thank you to the Red Bull Junior Team, my family, my support team @pbelm27 @papsc1 @lukeselbyosteopath , Mumbai Falcons, McLaren and to everyone who’s supported me along the way. Can’t wait to jump in the car soon!

P2 in Monaco😁✅ Feels great to be on the podium 🏆… A big congrats to the team @prema_team for a 1-2 finish! 
Next up ➡️ Feature Race
